                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">A judge makes decisions on disputed issues if parties cannot reach agreement.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start bg-rose-50 rounded-xl p-4">
                                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt text-rose-600 mr-3 mt-1"></i>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Longer Timeline</h4>
